These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros, bolivar, prince, vegafina, tiparillo, swisher
The people have 7 different hobbies: drawing, sudoku, card-games, gardening, magic-tricks, collecting, filmmaking
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess, scrabble, billiard, backgammon, bridge, canasta
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, subway, taxi, train, tram, van
 1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 2. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person driving the boat is the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 8. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
 9. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is the bolivar-smoker##1
12. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
13. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
14. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
15. the bolivar-smoker is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person driving the train##2
16. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
17. the prince-smoker is the person driving the train##1
18. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
19. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
20. the person who's hobby is collecting is the bolivar-smoker##1
21. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
22. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
23. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
24. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
25. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person playing chess##1
26. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |       3        |       4       |     5      |     6      |      7       |
| Cigar        | oliveros | tiparillo     | bolivar           | prince          | vegafina  | swisher | bluemaster         |
